M|Term|tx|These are the two commands qn runs on every single QA sn. Both must pass.
M|Term|tx|```bash
M|REQU|tx|npx tsc --noEmit
M|REQU|tx|npm run lint
M|REQU|tx|```
M|REQU|> No|Use `npx tsc --noEmit` in the Linux VM (SWC binary is Windows-only, `npm run bd` won't work here).
M|REQU|tx|> `npm run bd` must still pass on vc or a Windows machine before final dpl.
M|Comm|it|qn runs BOTH commands, in this order, every time
M|Comm|it|`npx tsc --noEmit` failing в†’ qn stops, reads the er, adds it to her вќЊ Bugs section w/ the fix proposal, issues blk
M|Comm|it|`npm run lint` failing в†’ qn stops, identifies which file and rule, adds to вќЊ section, issues blk
M|Comm|it|qn **never** issues APPROVED w/ a failing ts check or failing lint вЂ” no exceptions, no matter the reason
M|Comm|it|qn does not attempt to fix the code herself вЂ” she proposes the fix for rj or mi to im
M|How |tx|\| er Pattern \| Cause \| Assign To \|
M|How |tx|\|--------------\|-------\|-----------\|
M|How |tx|\| `tp X is not assignable to tp Y` \| ap rt rp doesn't match tp.ts \| rj \|
M|How |tx|\| `Property X does not exist on tp` \| Wrong tp assumption in cp \| mi (if in cp) or rj (if in rt) \|
M|How |tx|\| `Cannot find md` \| Missing import \| Whoever wrote the file w/ the bad import \|
M|How |tx|\| `Expected N arguments but got M` \| fn call signature mismatch \| Whoever wrote the calling code \|
M|How |tx|\| ESLint Rule \| Cause \| Assign To \|
M|How |tx|\|-------------\|-------\|-----------\|
M|How |tx|\| `@ts-eslint/no-explicit-any` \| `any` tp used \| rj (ap rt) or mi (cp) \|
M|How |tx|\| `rc-hooks/exhaustive-deps` \| Missing dependency in useEffect/useCallback \| mi \|
M|How |tx|\| `no-unused-vars` \| Imported but unused variable \| Whoever wrote the file \|
M|How |tx|\| `@nx/nx/no-img-element` \| Used `<img>` instead of nx.js `<im>` \| mi \|
